abstract: Four-time Olympic gold medalist Hayley Wickenheiser will not play for Canada in the women's world hockey championships due to foot surgery.
lead_paragraph: The four-time Olympic gold medalist Hayley Wickenheiser will not play for Canada in the women’s world hockey championships in Sweden in March.

headline.main: Canadian Women’s Hockey Star to Have Season-Ending Foot Surgery

snippet: The four-time Olympic gold medalist Hayley Wickenheiser will not play for Canada in the women’s world hockey championships in Sweden in March.
